I sincerely do enjoy this and I can tell it's had a lot of work put into it but I feel like it almost goes into a bit too much detail. Some of what entices me with an SCP is the inexplicable nature of its and the fact that it's often left up to the imagination, or just vague interpretation as to how certain aspects came to be, whereas this article feels like it rather readily explains it away immediately. This absolutely gets a +1 from me for the palpable amount of effort that was put into it, regardless.







